title: Help needed!! ASAP
body:
Dear community of EUW!

I am a 24 year old guy playing the league, but having trouble getting out of silver. I am not trying to blame my losses on anyone, but undeniably I meet a lot of trolls, afks, etc.
I am trying to find someone to duo with me, someone who is a jungle main maybe and has a lot of controll over the game, I promise I am not useless, we have the weekend to get to gold, I am S3 currently, PLS HELP!!!
Thanks in advance.

replies.body: Szerintem rossz fórumra írtál, mert ez EUNE és magyar.
